COUNT,SUM, AND AVERAGE OF POSITIVE AND NEGATIVE NUMBERS UNTIL USER GIVE [-1]

program:

positive_count = 0
negative_count = 0
positive_sum = 0
negative_sum = 0
num=int(input("Enter numbers (enter -1 to stop):")
while num != -1:
    if num > 0:
        positive_count += 1
        positive_sum += num
    elif num < 0:
        negative_count += 1
        negative_sum += num
    num = int(input("Enter numbers(enter -1 to stop):")

if positive_count > 0:
    positive_avg = positive_sum / positive_count
else:
    positive_avg = 0

if negative_count > 0:
    negative_avg = negative_sum / negative_count
else:
    negative_avg = 0

print("Number of positive numbers:", positive_count)
print("Sum of positive numbers:", positive_sum)
print("Average of positive numbers:", positive_avg)
print("Number of negative numbers:", negative_count)
print("Sum of negative numbers:", negative_sum)
print("Average of negative numbers:", negative_avg)

OUTPUT:

Enter numbers (enter -1 to stop):2
Enter numbers(enter -1 to stop):3
Enter numbers(enter -1 to stop):-5
Enter numbers(enter -1 to stop):-4
Enter numbers(enter -1 to stop):-1
Number of positive numbers: 2
Sum of positive numbers: 5
Average of positive numbers: 2.5
Number of negative numbers: 2
Sum of negative numbers: -9
Average of negative numbers: -4.5
